The '''Creative Workers Union of South Africa''' ('''CWUSA''') was a [[trade union]] in [[South Africa]]. It was affiliated with the [[Congress of South African Trade Unions]] (COSATU).<ref name="Cosatu affiliates list">{{cite web |url=http://www.cosatu.org.za/contact.php?id=42 |title=Creative Workers Union of South Africa |author=Cosatu |website=www.cosatu.org.za |accessdate=2 May 2014}}</ref> Its registration with the Department of Labour was cancelled on 9 May 2014<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.iol.co.za/news/politics/sacked-actors-union-not-registered-1740002|title=Sacked actorsâ€™ union not registered {{!}} IOL News|access-date=2018-05-13|language=en}}</ref>

